    "Jones cofounded two tech companies-Daisy Systems in 1981 and Tensilica in 1997.",
    "In between, he was CEO and chairman of electronic design automation company Synopsys, which now has a market cap of more than $80 billion.",
    "Jones is a billionaire almost entirely due to his Nvidia director's compensation. He owns 0.03% of the company.",
    "He continues to invest as a venture capitalist through his firm Square Wave Ventures."
